  {
    "id": "f_csv_8485c27ace",
    "slug": "sunny-put-on-eyebrows-eyelashes-makeup-matching-pajamas-a-silk-robe-and-the",
    "texto": "Sunny put on eyebrows, eyelashes, makeup, matching pajamas, a silk robe, and then say looking at herself in the vanity mirror in her bathroom. She had experienced moments in her life when she realized that she was actually alive and living in the world, instead of watching a movie starring herself, or narrating a book with herself as the main character. This was not one of those moments. She felt like she was drifting one centimeter above her physical self, a spirit at odds with its mechanical counterpart. She stood up carefully. Everything looked just right.",
